title: Even More Search Terms That Led People To This Blog
summary:
Key ideas 
- The author looks at search terms that lead people to their blog, including weird and inappropriate ones.
- The author lists misspelled versions of "Glasgow Coma Scale" that they found on their blog.
- The author makes humorous comments on some of the search terms.

Key learnings 
- Some people search for inappropriate and weird things on the internet.
- Misspellings of words can lead to completely different search results.
- The author has a humorous and sarcastic writing style.

Key questions 
- What motivates people to search for inappropriate content?
- How can misspellings of words affect search results?
- How can humor be used to address challenging topics?
